    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Water, earth, fire, and air. Master the four elements, and kill demons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious portal to hell has opened up and plunged the world into chaos. Only the Archetype, master of all four elements and legally distinct from the Avatar, can stop the demon invasion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fast 2D Shooter Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020370/extras/b9260374a3af67864087991e89f72fc7.poster.avif?t=1745512659\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020370/extras/b9260374a3af67864087991e89f72fc7.webm?t=1745512659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020370/extras/b9260374a3af67864087991e89f72fc7.mp4?t=1745512659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a variety of demons that challenge you to always be aware of your positioning, keep moving, prioritize enemies efficiently, and use all of the abilities in your arsenal. Master all of the elemental abilities to make quick work of the demon horde.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extremely Non-Linear<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020370/extras/3ba11f68a98d4bc1b863b05ed362dc6a.poster.avif?t=1745512659\" width=756 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020370/extras/3ba11f68a98d4bc1b863b05ed362dc6a.webm?t=1745512659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020370/extras/3ba11f68a98d4bc1b863b05ed362dc6a.mp4?t=1745512659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world is your oyster. Explore the world of this Metroidvania with little restriction on which direction you decide to explore in. Each ability you learn is a tool, not a key, and there are multiple solutions to every problem.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reincarnate Until You Succeed<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020370/extras/bbb2e7d588fc39b1e4010033ba75a1d3.poster.avif?t=1745512659\" width=800 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020370/extras/bbb2e7d588fc39b1e4010033ba75a1d3.webm?t=1745512659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020370/extras/bbb2e7d588fc39b1e4010033ba75a1d3.mp4?t=1745512659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game features a permadeath structure where you rotate through the four elements as starting areas, resulting in you learning different abilities first each run. Experience the remaining three areas differently based on the abilities you already have when you get there.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fourteen distinct enemy types that offer a wide variety of challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twelve elemental abilities that are all fun and expressive tools to use</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A combination of permadeath and nonlinear level design that makes each playthrough different</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A built-in item randomizer that unlocks once you’ve beaten the game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An original soundtrack that blends SNES-style chiptunes with heavy metal instrumentals</p></li></ul>",
